{"tid":632730,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"異度空間","createTime":"2018-04-17T16:15:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T08:25:09.000Z","uid":23734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"af957bd69d8c554c54e4e6a4531bf9b5e404fedf","tid":632730,"uid":23734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T16:15:35.000Z","msg":"今日屋企人出曬trip，啱啱心癮起，睇番一直好想睇但唔敢睇嘅異度空間，建議大家唔好自己一個一個人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一向都話哥哥拍完呢套戲之後，抽離唔到；原來以觀眾角度，睇呢套戲都會略略感受到<br />\n一邊睇，一邊諗，究竟哥哥係做緊戲，定係嗰個真係佢黎，尤其係佢自言自語同跳樓嗰兩幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇完套戲，播音樂嗰下，feel到自己好驚好恐怖，再加埋自己一個人係屋企，嗰種不安嘅情緒，好難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無睇過嘅巴打絲打有同感？"},{"pid":"44850a05fcaa0c94f430cc8bc788fd9b7690863d","tid":632730,"uid":43983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T16:28:06.000Z","msg":"呢套真係好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef5b75390d29bca51f6f6a0b76d97d42604aec1","tid":632730,"uid":127494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T16:28:18.000Z","msg":"證明咗哥哥對角色嘅投入度好高....<br />\n我睇又無咩feel"},{"pid":"b01546479c26ed7beb471d8ef0973002f8179cbf","tid":632730,"uid":23734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T16:31:08.000Z","msg":"如果現實都有個林嘉欣拉住哥哥就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195232d12bcdda7247a4c523fce10f7eec4a91a1","tid":632730,"uid":23734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T08:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}